Class pokerSuit

java.lang.Object
  pokerSuit

public class pokerSuit
extends java.lang.Object

Enumerates the 4 suits in a standard poker deck. The constructor is private. Each suit is represented by a static attribute, an instance of this class.

Author:
Kurt Schmidt
